name: 60-Second Fly Frenzy
description:
You have one minute to collect as many flies as possible, but catch a bee instead, or get hit by (dragonfly acid??) and it's game over!

How many can you grab before the time runs out?

Created for Frog Jam. My first time participating in a game jam! I had fun, I completed something in the span of 48 hours, and that's satisfying enough for me.

Made in Gamemaker Studio 2 (before I found out I didn't have the HTML export liscence )

My high score is 61, can you beat it?
